2 To amend and reenact R.S. 22:1452(C)(7) and 1454(B)(3) and to repeal R.S.
3 22:1452(C)(9.1), relative to insurer advertising expenses; to prevent the use of an
4 insurer's advertising expenses in determining its rates; to provide for definitions; and
5 to provide for related matters.
