DIGEST
SB 298 Original 2026 Regular Session Duplessis
Present law provides for items that may and may not be included in an insurer's rates.
Proposed law retains present law.
Proposed law prohibits an insurer from including advertising expenses in determining its
rates.
Present law defines "institutional advertising expenses". Proposed law repeals present law.
(Amends R.S. 22:1452(C)(7) and 1454(B)(3); repeals R.S. 22:1452(C)(9.1))
